e:T6f0,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Relume better than Stencil?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Relume scores 7.0 overall while Stencil scores 5.0. Relume is best for web designers and agencies, while Stencil excels for social media managers and bloggers."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Relume or Stencil?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Relume starts at Free and Stencil starts at Free. Relume offers a free plan. Stencil offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Relume to Stencil?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Relume and Stencil support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Relume vs Stencil?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Relume holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Stencil has an overall rating of 5/10 and ease of use score of 9/10. Users praise Relume for ai sitemap and wireframe generation and Stencil for extremely fast image creation."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Relume or Stencil?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Relume for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Stencil remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize extremely fast image creation. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$e"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"compare-header","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":[["$","h1",n